text: Josef Degeorgi (born 19 January 1960) is a former international Austrian footballer. Degeorgi won the Austrian league four times and the Austrian cup three times while playing for Austria Wien from 1983 to 1990. ==References== ==External links== * * Profile - Austria-archiv Category:1960 births Category:Living people Category:Austrian footballers Category:Austria international footballers Category:FK Austria Wien players Category:Austrian Football Bundesliga players Category:1982 FIFA World Cup players Category:Association football defenders
